218: Data/F4SE/Plugins/ for
219: version-specific code to
220: determine OG/NG support.
221: 
222: \N{HEAVY CHECK MARK} Version is supported
223: 
224: \N{CROSS MARK} Version not supported
225: 
226: \N{BLACK QUESTION MARK ORNAMENT} Not an F4SE DLL.
